<h2>3: Gap Creek Road to below Dead Man's Curve (Rte 41 at Rte 97 to SR288 at Rte 175)</h2>
<table class='data_table river-stats'>
<tr class='row-1'>
<th>Usual Difficulty</th>
<td>II-III (for normal flows) </td>
</tr>
